# Server Templates Directory

This directory is for server-specific template overrides.

## Purpose

Templates placed here will take priority over shared templates in `../static/`.

## Usage

To customize the email UI:

```bash
# Copy the default template
cp ../static/ui_all.html templates/ui_all.html

# Edit your custom version
nano templates/ui_all.html
```

## Template Search Priority

1. **`server/templates/`** ← Checked first (this directory)
2. **`../static/`** ← Fallback if not found here

## Example

If both exist:
- `server/templates/ui_all.html` ✅ (used)
- `../static/ui_all.html` (ignored)

If only fallback exists:
- `server/templates/ui_all.html` (doesn't exist)
- `../static/ui_all.html` ✅ (used)

This allows you to override only the templates you need to customize!
